TokenProps.name: variant
TokenProps.deprecated:
The `'disabled'` and `'focused'` variants have been deprecated and will be
removed in a future version. Please use the `disabled` and `focused` boolean
props instead.

**Before**

`<Token variant="disabled|focused" />`

**After**

`<Token disabled focused />`
